skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: silly billy
des: The classic game of repeat after me, but you get to pick the words. Alexa will start with one random word for you to repeat and then add to the list of words. See how many words you can repeat correctly! Choose a list of words to have some very funny phrases!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
